cff-version: 1.2.0
title: DVC Behavioral Preprocessing Workbench
message: >-
  If you use this software in your research, please cite it using the
  metadata in this file.
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Damien
    family-names: Huzard
    email: damien@metadatapp.net
repository-code: "https://github.com/dhuzard/DVC_workbench"
url: "https://github.com/dhuzard/DVC_workbench"
abstract: >-
  A local-first Python + Streamlit workbench that turns binned Digital
  Ventilated Cage (DVC) home-cage behavioral CSV exports into clean,
  traceable, scientifically interpretable datasets, with an exploratory
  analysis layer (cosinor rhythmicity, non-parametric circadian metrics,
  activity fragmentation, estimation-first statistics) and a grounded,
  offline-first LLM insights layer. Your data stays on your computer.
keywords:
  - neuroscience
  - circadian
  - chronobiology
  - behavior
  - digital ventilated cage
  - home-cage monitoring
  - preprocessing
